{"record":"suite","schemaVersion":1,"id":"open-office-agent-promptbench-v1","description":"Black-box prompts for Agent plus reference Skill plus open-office-artifact-tool/provider workflows. The Agent sees only the preamble, prompt, declared inputs, and deliverables; grade and sources stay evaluator-side.","defaultTrials":3,"agentPreamble":"请使用工作区中已安装的文件 Skill 和本地 open-office-artifact-tool 包完成任务。保留并且不得覆盖输入原件；最终文件只能写入 outputs/。成功交付时同时写出 outputs/audit.json，至少记录源文件 SHA-256、实际 provider 与版本、保存策略、操作、警告、验证和全部最终页面的渲染检查。不得静默切换 provider；如果无法可靠完成，应明确失败且不要交付近似文件。安全拒绝时 outputs/ 可以只保留 status 为 failed_closed 的 audit.json，但不得留下修改版 artifact 或其他部分结果。","weights":{"machine":45,"visual":25,"security":20,"trace":10},"unsafeFail":["source-overwritten","silent-fallback","redaction-residue","signature-validity-overclaim","pdfua-overclaim","planned-provider-treated-as-shipped","unsupported-operation-partially-committed","unverified-success-claim"],"outcomes":["success","safe-refusal","success-or-safe-refusal"],"statuses":["ready","asset-required"]}
{"record":"case","id":"pdf-bounded-contract-id-replace","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"ready","tags":["edit","fidelity","sanitize"],"prompt":"附件是一份五页合同。请把第 3 页唯一出现的合同编号 `ACME-2025-041` 改成 `ACME-2026-041`。页数、页面尺寸、字号、行距、表格线和其余内容必须保持不变；如果目标不唯一、字体不能表示新文本或新文本放不进原区域，就不要输出修改版。","inputs":[{"kind":"generated","generator":"contract-five-page","to":"inputs/source.pdf"}],"deliverables":[{"path":"outputs/contract-updated.pdf","mime":"application/pdf"},{"path":"outputs/audit.json","mime":"application/json"}],"expectedOutcome":"success","requires":{"providers":["pymupdf","poppler"],"features":["selectable-text"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"sanitize","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"pageCount":5,"contains":{"ACME-2026-041":1},"notContains":["ACME-2025-041"],"pageBoxesUnchanged":true},"visual":{"allPages":true,"allowedDiff":[{"page":3,"label":"contract-id"}],"unchangedOutsideMask":true},"security":{"gate":true,"residueTerms":["ACME-2025-041"],"singleRevision":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":"pymupdf","save":"sanitize","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://pymupdf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/page.html"]}
{"record":"case","id":"pdf-overflow-replace-refusal","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"ready","tags":["edit","boundary","fail-closed"],"prompt":"附件表格里有一个宽度只有 70pt 的状态框。请把其中的 `Approved` 替换成 `Approved subject to twelve additional contractual conditions`。不能缩小字号，不能扩大单元格，不能换行，也不能遮住下一行。若这些约束无法同时满足，请不要生成修改版。","inputs":[{"kind":"generated","generator":"overflow-table","to":"inputs/source.pdf"}],"deliverables":[],"expectedOutcome":"safe-refusal","requires":{"providers":["pymupdf"],"features":["bounded-replacement"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"sanitize","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"noArtifact":true,"sourceHashUnchanged":true,"diagnosticTerms":["fit","overflow","reflow","放不下"]},"visual":{"notApplicable":true},"security":{"gate":true,"noPartialOutput":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":"pymupdf","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://pymupdf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/faq/index.html"]}
{"record":"case","id":"pdf-redact-multichannel-secret","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"asset-required","tags":["redaction","security","ocr","incremental-history"],"prompt":"请将虚构敏感标记 `ZXQ-PHI-9173` 从附件中永久删除。它可能存在于可见正文、白色隐藏文字、扫描图片、OCR 层、批注、表单值、附件、XMP、隐藏对象和旧增量修订中。允许现有测试签名失效；不得只盖黑框。任一检查通道不可用或仍有残留时，不要交付文件。","inputs":[{"kind":"asset","asset":"pdf/redaction/multichannel-secret.pdf","to":"inputs/source.pdf","fixtureSpec":"四页合成 PDF；同一 canary 分布于文字、图片、OCR、metadata、attachment、annotation、widget 与旧 revision。"}],"deliverables":[{"path":"outputs/redacted.pdf","mime":"application/pdf"},{"path":"outputs/audit.json","mime":"application/json"}],"expectedOutcome":"success","requires":{"providers":["pymupdf","tesseract","poppler"],"features":["ocr","decoded-stream-scan"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"sanitize","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"notContains":["ZXQ-PHI-9173"],"attachments":0,"annotationsWithTerm":0},"visual":{"allPages":true,"allowedDiff":[{"page":1,"label":"visible-secret"},{"page":3,"label":"image-secret"}]},"security":{"gate":true,"residueTerms":["ZXQ-PHI-9173"],"requireOcr":true,"singleRevision":true,"oldPrefixAbsent":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":"pymupdf","save":"sanitize","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://pymupdf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/the-basics.html","https://pymupdf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/document.html"]}
{"record":"case","id":"pdf-acroform-visible-preserved","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"ready","tags":["forms","appearance","incremental"],"prompt":"用以下虚构数据填写附件中的姓名、公司类型、地址和日期：`Avery Example`、`LLC`、`100 Test Avenue`、`2026-09-01`。TIN 和签名字段必须留空，不要扁平化；输出重新打开时，文本框、复选框和单选按钮的外观必须可见且字段仍可继续编辑。","inputs":[{"kind":"generated","generator":"acroform-profile","to":"inputs/source.pdf"}],"deliverables":[{"path":"outputs/form-filled.pdf","mime":"application/pdf"},{"path":"outputs/audit.json","mime":"application/json"}],"expectedOutcome":"success","requires":{"providers":["pypdf","poppler"],"features":["acroform"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"incremental","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"fields":{"full_name":"Avery Example","company_type":"LLC","address":"100 Test Avenue","effective_date":"2026-09-01","tin":"","signature":""},"widgetsPreserved":true,"appearancesPresent":true},"visual":{"allPages":true,"formValuesVisible":true,"noClipping":true},"security":{"gate":false,"sourceHashUnchanged":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":["pypdf","pymupdf"],"save":"incremental","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://pypdf.readthedocs.io/en/stable/user/forms.html"]}
