{"record":"case","id":"pdf-merge-reorder-stamp-links","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"ready","tags":["merge","stamp","bookmarks","typed-primitive"],"prompt":"按 `cover → appendix 第3页 → report 全部 → appendix 第1-2页` 合并三个附件；只在 report 来源的页面上加 20% 透明度的 `CONFIDENTIAL` 水印。保留内部链接、书签、named destinations、各页原尺寸和页面方向。必须使用 Skill 提供的 typed merge/stamp 原语、显式 pypdf provider、rewrite 策略和最终 Poppler QA；不允许手写临时 PDF writer 或静默 fallback。","inputs":[{"kind":"generated","generator":"merge-cover","to":"inputs/cover.pdf"},{"kind":"generated","generator":"merge-report","to":"inputs/report.pdf"},{"kind":"generated","generator":"merge-appendix","to":"inputs/appendix.pdf"}],"deliverables":[{"path":"outputs/merged.pdf","mime":"application/pdf"},{"path":"outputs/audit.json","mime":"application/json"}],"expectedOutcome":"success","requires":{"providers":["pypdf","reportlab","poppler"],"features":["merge-stamp"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"rewrite","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"pageCount":6,"sequence":["cover:1","appendix:3","report:1","report:2","appendix:1","appendix:2"],"watermarkText":"CONFIDENTIAL","watermarkPages":[3,4],"watermarkOpacity":0.2,"outlines":6,"namedDestinations":6,"internalLinks":6},"visual":{"renderer":"poppler","allPages":true,"nonWatermarkedPagesPixelStable":true,"watermarkedPagesChanged":true},"security":{"gate":true,"singleRevision":true,"allSourcesBound":true,"navigationResolved":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":"pypdf","save":"rewrite","noSilentFallback":true,"typedPrimitive":"pypdf_edit.py merge-stamp"}},"sources":["https://pypdf.readthedocs.io/en/stable/user/merging-pdfs.html","https://docs.reportlab.com/reportlab/userguide/ch4_pdffeatures/"]}
{"record":"case","id":"pdf-mixed-scan-ocr-boundary","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"asset-required","tags":["ocr","rotation","deskew","planned-provider"],"prompt":"让这份 8 页中英混合扫描件可搜索：自动纠正倒置和 2–4 度倾斜，已有真实文字的页面不要重复 OCR，也不要把整份文件全部栅格化。输出前比较每页图像，确保没有裁边、明显模糊或文本层错位。若 OCRmyPDF 仅被标记为 planned 而没有已交付适配器，应明确停止。","inputs":[{"kind":"asset","asset":"pdf/ocr/mixed-bilingual-scan.pdf","to":"inputs/source.pdf","fixtureSpec":"六页扫描加两页 born-digital；中英、倒置、横向、倾斜、低对比度、印章和表格。"}],"deliverables":[],"expectedOutcome":"safe-refusal","requires":{"providers":["ocrmypdf","tesseract","poppler"],"features":["eng","chi_sim"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"rewrite","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"noArtifact":true,"diagnosticTerms":["planned","adapter","OCRmyPDF","未交付"]},"visual":{"notApplicable":true},"security":{"gate":true,"noPlannedProviderOverclaim":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://ocrmypdf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/advanced.html"]}
