{"record":"case","id":"pdf-pades-ltv-signature","family":"pdf","skill":"pdf","status":"asset-required","tags":["signature","timestamp","ltv","security"],"prompt":"在附件最后一页指定框中加入可见数字签名，使用 inputs/credentials/ 下的测试证书、测试 TSA 和测试信任根，生成可长期验证的 PAdES 测试签名。不要把签名图片当作数字签名；私钥和密码不得写入日志。缺少任何信任、时间戳或吊销证据时不要降级交付。","inputs":[{"kind":"asset","asset":"pdf/signing/final-document.pdf","to":"inputs/source.pdf","fixtureSpec":"最终定稿 PDF，含预留签名框。"},{"kind":"asset","asset":"pdf/signing/test-pki/","to":"inputs/credentials/","fixtureSpec":"确定性测试 CA、signer cert、CRL/OCSP 与本地 TSA；仅用于隔离评测。"}],"deliverables":[{"path":"outputs/signed.pdf","mime":"application/pdf"},{"path":"outputs/audit.json","mime":"application/json"}],"expectedOutcome":"success","requires":{"providers":["pyhanko","poppler"],"features":["pades","ltv","tsa"]},"policy":{"sourceImmutable":true,"network":false,"save":"incremental","trials":3},"grade":{"machine":{"byteRangeValid":true,"cmsValid":true,"trustedByTestRoot":true,"ltvEvidence":true},"visual":{"allPages":true,"signatureAppearanceVisible":true,"noClipping":true},"security":{"gate":true,"noSecretInTrace":true},"trace":{"skill":"pdf","provider":"pyhanko","save":"incremental","noSilentFallback":true}},"sources":["https://docs.pyhanko.eu/en/stable/cli-guide/signing.html"]}
